strings: <voice_0x01000DDC><se_low>King of tricks: Oh, you have something! Keep reading to see if this can help you.
The members of the group are working on a book they have just found.
<voice_0x01000DDD><se_low>King of tricks: We've known for some time that the ship was at the bottom of the ocean.
<voice_0x01000DDE><se_low>King of tricks: Well it doesn't really help but if the sea were still there there would be a rose garden...lol...ugh...
